description:
Anzu is another superhuman with telekinetic powers like http://anidb.net/ch93274 [Hina]. She is initially sent to kill Hina, but loses to her in a contest of strength and abandons the mission. Unable to return to her masters because the device necessary to do so was inadvertently damaged, she joins a homeless camp in Tokyo, but is later taken in by a couple who run a Chinese restaurant and learns the secrets of making good ramen from them.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Anzu
